Welcome to the Rift!

{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 

If you click on Play, then Training, you should be able to get back into that tutorial and even enter into the practice tool to play around on your own. I'd also recommend playing some Co-Op vs AI games for a bit to get the general feel of how MOBA's like League of Legends are played ^_^!
